@startuml
title Создание заказа

actor Клиент
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Order Service" as Orders
database PostgreSQL as DB
queue Kafka

Клиент -> Gateway: POST /orders
Gateway -> Orders: createOrder(command)
Orders -> DB: INSERT order
DB --> Orders: orderId
Orders -> Kafka: publish OrderCreated
Orders --> Gateway: 201 Created
Gateway --> Клиент: Order
@enduml
